Place all the ingredients except the salmon and noodles into a pan, adding a little water, if necessary, to completely cover the ingredients. Bring to the boil, reduce the heat and simmer for 4-5 minutes.Add the salmon to the broth and simmer for 3-4 minutes, or until the salmon is cooked through and the broccoli is tender. Add the noodles and stir to mix.To serve, pour the broth into a bowl.